Create table:-
mybook 
having attributes:-
1)book_id (varchar(20)) (primary key)
2)book_name (varchar(100))
3)author (varchar(100))
4)publicatin (varchar(100))
5)cost (int)
6)edition (int)
 
user
 having attributes:-
1)user_name (varchar(100)) (primary key) (email id)
2)password (varchar(50))

Perform CURD operation

1)Book
2)BookService
  *verifyUser(username,pass) boolean
  *deleteBook(book_id)
  *fetchBookByBookId(book_id)
  *updateBook(Book)
  *fetchAllBook()
  *fetchBookByAuthor(author)
